{"tid":52160,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩去過美國exchange 既入一入黎","createTime":"2016-12-23T21:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:10:30.000Z","uid":53748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3285358973df710f83fb8ae531574a83127e9eb0","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T21:28:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 小弟黎緊去美國exchange 一個sem<br />\n但係唔知應該點樣係當地洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我得一張恆生enjoy 卡, 同hsbc 既提款卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始係香港會唱定少少錢先入美國<br />\n用晒之後, 平時買野應該用credit card 抵啲<br />\n定係去禁hsbc 機拎錢抵啲<br />\n定係係美國申請張debit card 抵啲?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n申請多張大新既國際學生master card 有無so?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"55a48edb70aa063d7abc331a20ebeb592018b7df","tid":52160,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T22:48:55.000Z","msg":"美國唔清楚，不過北美多用debit card，好小人用cash。可以整個bank account，走時先cancel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過走之前記住洗到淨翻幾仙先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f288654d756314c54d43110e7064f3a76c9c53d","tid":52160,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"用香港既卡可能每一次都會收你手續費<br />\n<br />\n去到開張 debit card 啦<br />\n<br />\n衣食住行既野，其實最好係問下當地既 香港學生會 /  華人教會 / 強國 學生會"},{"pid":"69352b29711823f639d557d36b5549acd6ab83c2","tid":52160,"uid":61559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"開張debit card<br />\n如果想㩒錢最平應該係用香港銀聯提款卡去citibank㩒（冇記錯得citibank支援銀聯提款）"},{"pid":"0497be8aca6b8a0a60f155b184c97213c0301828","tid":52160,"uid":27885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:23:04.000Z","msg":"開張卡 電匯"},{"pid":"11931f4c66e950b419e0a60ef1140d189a1992ee","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T20:45:55.000Z","msg":"即係係美國開戶口, 整張debit card, 然後香港戶口過數去美國戶口, 再用debit card 買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> debit card 可唔可以禁錢出來?<br />\n<br />\n對唔住, 小弟真係唔識呢方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28c1076e383ae4f2a27f0bb892584d33dabcc17","tid":52160,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T20:51:50.000Z","msg":"用卡啦，果邊買嘢有稅，計毫子袋大餅好撚煩的。或者你將啲錢入定落Visa/Master 嘅信用卡咪得囉。(不過唔知要收幾多手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n或者好似樓上啲巴打咁提議，去到開個戶口。去櫃員機攞錢方面就一定係Visa/Master/Plus方便嫁喇，受銀聯嘅機好似比較少。<br />\n<br />\nBetween，上Amazon買嘢一了百了，冇稅又方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：美洲非美國exchange"},{"pid":"9cc1eab84760168632227b044b99834c941b8bee","tid":52160,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T20:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係係美國開戶口, 整張debit card, 然後香港戶口過數去美國戶口, 再用debit card 買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> debit card 可唔可以禁錢出來?<br />\n<br />\n對唔住, 小弟真係唔識呢方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求鳩其去chase或者local 啲既credit union 去開就得，十五分鍾批核，廿四小時可用，之後用routing number過數。<br />\nDebit card ~ 存左錢既credit card, 不過除左搭巴士同叫雞，你應該冇咩機會用到cash.<br />\n<br />\n利申: 人在美帝。"},{"pid":"af4d36a41196424ff0c7f5bba27b81faa379a57b","tid":52160,"uid":15650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T21:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係係美國開戶口, 整張debit card, 然後香港戶口過數去美國戶口, 再用debit card 買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> debit card 可唔可以禁錢出來?<br />\n<br />\n對唔住, 小弟真係唔識呢方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀 係美國開咗bank of America 嘅debit card, 開咗之後佢會俾個swift code同routing account 俾你, 你只要去返香港任何一間大銀行滙錢就得(無論滙幾多錢 都係收同樣價錢嘅手續費) debit card可以㩒錢出黎嘅, 其實debit card 姐係香港嘅eps<br />\n<br />\n利申 係美國東岸讀左幾年 有唔明歡迎繼續問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd86369054fc771ceed8f527a184503f7cc2850e","tid":52160,"uid":65736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7ddfe95b94bea0035612de20afeef622e2bc5ce9","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:29:10.000Z","msg":"唔該晒咁多位巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有問題遲啲再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cad4071d84914744caf5bccbe51bcf1f79a8b1","tid":52160,"uid":53080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"我都係去us exchange<br />\n淨係開左citi bank acc<br />\n諗住去到再係bank of America開acc"},{"pid":"0ae5b202be315432d9c56653cb4763e4adbc9be0","tid":52160,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T07:50:40.000Z","msg":"如果係香港有HSBC户口可以幫你開HSBC US户口不過要畀錢 但係Prime 户口可以免費"},{"pid":"cb529e09e032cdd1c7e9a4b16f6d8a97b4212c41","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係香港有HSBC户口可以幫你開HSBC US户口不過要畀錢 但係Prime 户口可以免費</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打, 但係學校果區都無hsbc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0758b3f8af23077a791ec13e8f32762032bcb678","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:51:48.000Z","msg":"而家諗住去到開citibank 戶口整張 debit card, 到時香港hsbc 戶口轉賬過去<br />\n<br />\n想問下, 香港果邊係hkd, 轉過去計做usd, 定我要係香港轉定做usd 先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8864e60bd420184368cf6b2a10033446be245fb9","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家諗住去到開citibank 戶口整張 debit card, 到時香港hsbc 戶口轉賬過去<br />\n<br />\n想問下, 香港果邊係hkd, 轉過去計做usd, 定我要係香港轉定做usd 先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋手續費係咪hsbc 同citibank 都會charge 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07ed7598c24fc7721580ddbde34ba299f1a6902","tid":52160,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afda6a31f6c40ed9bc36e831123cefa890acbc05","tid":52160,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n如果想用Credit Card<br />\n可以試下申請Citibank Thank You Preferred Card for International Student (用緊)<br />\n<br />\nBoA都有credit card for international student<br />\n不過前提係你要有BoA account(好似係)同入面要有錢"},{"pid":"f4d29c97d9dbe390d78c22ea5c7fb1f4f00c0ee6","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家諗住去到開citibank 戶口整張 debit card, 到時香港hsbc 戶口轉賬過去<br />\n<br />\n想問下, 香港果邊係hkd, 轉過去計做usd, 定我要係香港轉定做usd 先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋手續費係咪hsbc 同citibank 都會charge 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20ed8ce4c76bc7dd7474f05b33f2062f64c6196","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無citibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又就飛, 應該整唔切"},{"pid":"e2f831c3617afc2fa6b0e8163e71db457f846baa","tid":52160,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無citibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又就飛, 應該整唔切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開個account好快姐嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0865fc5780c3de737747ba9663918ce445820fd5","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無citibank<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又就飛, 應該整唔切</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開個account好快姐嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我後日去citibank 問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94610eb3c3c04bb511db44ca85c9535a8140091","tid":52160,"uid":53748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T19:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張卡同保安編碼趕得切到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒巴打<br />\n<br />\n仲想問, 個香港戶口要唔要開海外提款<br />\n定到時去到美國開左debit card 先用環球理財服務link 左港美acct 佢?<br />\n<br />\n同埋知唔知, 美國戶口trans 返錢去香港果個收唔收手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕最後有錢剩係美國acct 拎唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大感謝巴打"},{"pid":"ddfea24f84dd7e91178b0a863e14a0a534b1c6bd","tid":52160,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喺美國Citibank開學生account之後拎埋Debit Card<br />\n叫呀爸呀媽喺香港Citibank開個account申請環球理財服務<br />\n轉賬去美國Citibank account 豁免手續費<br />\n比錢乜乜乜都用Debit Card<br />\nDebit Card可以拎錢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 美國留學第三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張卡同保安編碼趕得切到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該晒巴打<br />\n<br />\n仲想問, 個香港戶口要唔要開海外提款<br />\n定到時去到美國開左debit card 先用環球理財服務link 左港美acct 佢?<br />\n<br />\n同埋知唔知, 美國戶口trans 返錢去香港果個收唔收手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕最後有錢剩係美國acct 拎唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大感謝巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港戶口唔洗開海外提款<br />\n因為你喺美國唔會用香港張卡<br />\n你到咗美國開咗新Citibank Account之後咪用環球理財服務由香港轉錢過嚟囉<br />\n<br />\n轉返錢過香港我就唔知 因為我未試過 不過美國都有Global Transfers服務<br />\n<a href=\"https://online.citi.com/US/JRS/pands/detail.do?ID=InterCiti&amp;JFP_TOKEN=FFSHCQQA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonline.citi.com%2FUS%2FJRS%2Fpands%2Fdetail.do%3FID%3DInterCiti%26JFP_TOKEN%3DFFSHCQQA&d=CqmD8etZWLr3H89FsyW3gEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=cb98faf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://online.citi.com/US/JRS/pands/detail.do?ID=InterCiti&amp;JFP_TOKEN=FFSHCQQA</a><br />\n佢寫住:<br />\n<strong>What it Costs</strong><br />\nIncoming transfers free.<br />\nOutgoing domestic transfers free.<br />\n<em>Outgoing international transfers, no transfer fee.</em><br />\n所以我諗轉返香港應該唔使錢"},{"pid":"2050a0e97a2aa93d63d40b618e3ce247d00218d5","tid":52160,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-13T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"Btw 巴打去美國邊忽exchange?"}]}